messages.text: On difficult days, remember that you've overcome challenges before. Your resilience is stronger than you might feel right now.

One effective coping strategy is the 5-4-3-2-1 grounding technique: Acknowledge 5 things you see, 4 things you can touch, 3 things you can hear, 2 things you can smell, and 1 thing you can taste. This helps bring you back to the present moment.
